"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aed4c3f9d7a3c05fccf6155817c0f92894068063","tid":1833764,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T06:01:31.000Z","msg":"商標註冊維護成本好高，因為要搵人check 住個list 有冇撞，撞左又要搵人反駁<br />\n<br />\n所以中小企會直接忽略，好似龍門冰室咁<br />\n<br />\n搞到要出聲明，明顯係抬底拆唔掂<br />\n<br />\n好多時轉個新logo，公關上轉新型象，肯和解就咩事都冇"},{"pid":"84eb0b1cdd916b08274187c221184c624e86dd01","tid":1833764,"uid":44160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T06:02:42.000Z","msg":"愈爆愈多犯法野，不知所謂"},{"pid":"82ef716b446a594f0d879137ea2d084c3c981c6f","tid":1833764,"uid":215876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"84eb0b1cdd916b08274187c221184c624e86dd01","tid":1833764,"uid":44160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T06:02:42.000Z","msg":"愈爆愈多犯法野，不知所謂"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T06:04:16.000Z","msg":"符合警隊形象<br />\n知法犯法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"783f734cf6f6b7ea596883a27ed2a1cd589828cb","tid":1833764,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"84eb0b1cdd916b08274187c221184c624e86dd01","tid":1833764,"uid":44160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T06:02:42.000Z","msg":"愈爆愈多犯法野，不知所謂"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T06:18:53.000Z","msg":"自己攞嚟衰<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5457819c158ebb6bbabe29c89a702799ee1411a8","tid":1833764,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T06:20:00.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"d45a9ee0cddfe61b70bdd883090e32d4d3909f85","tid":1833764,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"8da8cf831bd7335a2473f592a393e1ead4b64908","tid":1833764,"uid":250849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T05:37:30.000Z","msg":"藍象係咩黎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif